      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:2:82:2",
      "text": [
        " عِدَّةُ الْعِلْجَةِ إِذَا أَسْلَمَتْ عِدَّةُ الْمُطَلَّقَةِ إِذَا أَرَادَتْ أَنْ تَتَزَوَّجَ غَيْرَهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ismail Bin Marrar, from Yunus, ",
          "‘He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘A waiting period of the الْعِلْجَةِ when she becomes a Muslim, is a waiting period of the divorced woman, when she intends to marry someone else’."
        ]
      }
